'phyloseq' object for the data published in Fitzpatrick et al. (2018) after removing DNA contamination.

psE_BARBI.Rd

A 'phyloseq' class object with 5808 taxa in 86 samples that are from seven rounds of six-fold dilutions (1:1 up to 1:279,936) from standard ZymoBIOMICS microbial community and 10 negative extraction controls.

psE_BARBI

Format

An object of class 'phyloseq'.

SampleType

Whether Asteraceae or non-Asteraceae

pna

Type of pPNA used universal or Asteraceae-modified

species_names

Sample ID

Source

Fitzpatrick et al. (2018)

Examples

if (FALSE) {
sample_data(psE_BARBI)
otu_table(psE_BARBI)
}
